about.summary: Provides an 'R' interface to the 'NiftyReg' image registration tools <http://sourceforge.net/projects/niftyreg/>. Linear and nonlinear registration are supported, in two and three dimensions.

name: r-rniftyreg
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.6.8" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rniftyreg
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/RNiftyReg_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/RNiftyReg/RNiftyReg_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c409d5f8a73dec59ddc1961315b58903bb8b634154cee98be1f2707a7f9191a6

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}            # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_cxx') }}      # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}grep              # [win]
    - {{ posix }}autoconf
    - {{ posix }}automake          # [not win]
    - {{ posix }}automake-wrapper  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}pkg-config
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-rnifti >=0.4.0
    - r-rcpp >=0.11.0
    - r-rcppeigen
    - r-ore
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]
    - r-rnifti >=0.4.0
    - r-rcpp >=0.11.0
    - r-rcppeigen
    - r-ore

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('RNiftyReg')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('RNiftyReg')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/jonclayden/RNiftyReg
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Provides an 'R' interface to the 'NiftyReg' image registration tools <http://sourceforge.net/projects/niftyreg/>. Linear and nonlinear registration are
    supported, in two and three dimensions.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
